00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:15.920
Rhyw Groeslyn, yna.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:17.920
Cwneungod i gyd ag annog ffordd a mixymotosis.

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:20.920
Yn tri os o'n mynd oedd o'n mynd dros yna.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:22.920
O, bechal.

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:24.920
O, o'n lwg a diawel ar y ffeil yna amser,

00:06:24.920 --> 00:06:26.920
ni ap ag wydol ffordd yna.

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:28.920
A'n mixymotosis amdano'n i gyd.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:32.920
Mi'n gorio ti ddweud y stori.

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:34.920
A oedd o'n ti cofio gwyn ar y ffordd i Aberystwyth?

00:06:36.920 --> 00:06:38.920
Ar ochr y ffordd?

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.920
